                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10062" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0389</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">412 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">以柔克刚：吉利动力柔性化改造的升级之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Overcoming Rigidity with Flexibility:The Upgrading Road of Geely Powertrain&#39;s Flexible Transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">舒湘沅，张敬昱，张海阔</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江吉利动力总成有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">柔性化改造；柔性制造；吉利动力；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">flexible transformation; flexible manufacturing; Geely Powertrain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在全球碳中和浪潮的影响下，新能源车渗透率提升以及消费需求的多样化促使汽车市场形成了燃油车、混动/增程车、纯电动车相互包容、协同发展的格局，以多品种、小批量、快速调整为特征的柔性制造模式成为汽车制造企业生存和致胜的关键。本案例以吉利动力为例，呈现了吉利动力GEP3平台装配生产线柔性化改造的过程，描述了吉利动力是如何围绕工艺设备柔性化、信息系统柔性化、产线布局柔性化以及设计与制造协同柔性化来实现柔性制造的，并最终成功完成了BHE15系列机型与GEP3系列机型共线生产的任务。通过本案例的学习和讨论，旨在帮助学生深入理解柔性制造的内涵，引导学生探索柔性化改造的内外部因素、思考企业应如何突破产线生产瓶颈，明晰柔性化改造能够为企业带来的积极效果。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Amid the global wave of carbon neutrality, the increasing penetration rate of new energy vehicles and diversified consumer demands have fostered a collaborative and synergistic landscape in the automotive market, where fuel vehicles, hybrid/range-extended vehicles, and pure electric vehicles coexist. In this context, flexible manufacturing characterized by multi-variety, low-volume production, and rapid adaptability has become a critical survival and competitive strategy for automotive manufacturers. This case study focuses on Geely Powertrain’s flexible transformation of the GEP3 platform assembly line, detailing how the company achieved co-production of BHE15 and GEP3 engine series through innovations in four key areas: process equipment flexibility, information system flexibility, production layout flexibility, and design-manufacturing collaboration flexibility. By analyzing this transformation, the case aims to help students deeply understand the essence of flexible manufacturing, explore internal and external drivers of such transformations, reflect on strategies to overcome production bottlenecks, and recognize the positive impacts of flexibility on enterprise competitiveness.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《生产运作管理》、《运营管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">柔性制造的概念；柔性制造的评价指标；制造柔性的维度划分；资源编排理论；制造柔性的功能构成</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
